独立的数字生命？还是我在数字世界中继续活着呢？\r\n\r\n为什么想到这种问题，反而让我觉得有点伤感？","content_rendered":"<p>摸鱼中，突然想到这件事。</p>\n<p>我在想，如果 GPT 能不停的录入视频训练数据（先忽略成本），从现在开始把我每天的出门回家、工作、与他人对话聊天所见所闻都录进去。假设 50 年后我去世，数字世界是否能根据数据训练出另一个“我”？性格相同，爱好相同，记忆中的事与物也相同。</p>\n<p>而新产生的另一个“我”，是一个全新的、独立的数字生命？还是我在数字世界中继续活着呢？</p>\n<p>为什么想到这种问题，反而让我觉得有点伤感？</p>\n","last_modified":1679299876,"replies":25,"id":925585},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":199811,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3743,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":515568,"username":"AMZsowhat","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/AMZsowhat","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/afb3/d156/515568_mini.png?m=1676965505","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/afb3/d156/515568_normal.png?m=1676965505","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/afb3/d156/515568_large.png?m=1676965505","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/afb3/d156/515568_xlarge.png?m=1676965505","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/afb3/d156/515568_xlarge.png?m=1676965505","created":1604283759,"last_modified":1676965505},"last_reply_by":"AMZsowhat","last_touched":1679305873,"title":"大家平时都在吃什么零食?","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/925582","created":1679299582,"deleted":0,"content":"如题,准备买一点超级干的牛肉干和黑巧,突然想到就,问下大家还有什么好吃的","content_rendered":"如题,准备买一点超级干的牛肉干和黑巧,突然想到就,问下大家还有什么好吃的","last_modified":1679300018,"replies":22,"id":925582},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png