739760","name":"career","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1670739760","title":"职场话题","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","topics":14109,"footer":"","header":"这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。","title_alternative":"Career","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1670739760","stars":2636,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":770,"parent_node_name":"work"},"member":{"id":565467,"username":"cangcang","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/cangcang","website":null,"twitter":"5UtHp0tGBVg5uod","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3559/efb2/565467_mini.png?m=1679305831","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3559/efb2/565467_normal.png?m=1679305831","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3559/efb2/565467_large.png?m=1679305831","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3559/efb2/565467_xlarge.png?m=1679305831","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3559/efb2/565467_xlarge.png?m=1679305831","avatar_xxxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3559/efb2/565467_xlarge.png?m=1679305831","created":1639482189,"last_modified":1679305831},"last_reply_by":"DAMNYOU","last_touched":1679314152,"title":"升职不加薪怎么办","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/925631","created":1679307361,"deleted":0,"content":"## 概要\r\n- 二线城市小作坊，入职一年多\r\n\r\n- 我司前端部门原本没有负责人，一直是我在主导\r\n\r\n- 今年春节后，领导开会指定我虚线带队\r\n\r\n- 事后找领导谈加薪，让我等到 7 月份\r\n\r\n## 想法\r\n入职以来我一直有在好好努力提升技能，为公司解决了很多的技术难题，就算不升职也该加薪了。\r\n\r\n当初入职之前谈好的是 13k ，入职后硬是砍了我 1k ，这件事一直让我如鲠在喉。\r\n\r\n想立刻跳槽，但又对‘等 7 月份’这个饼抱有幻想。一直催眠自己，诸如[累积带队经验对以后有帮助]\r\n\r\n**各位大佬能不能给点建议，或分享一下类似的经历**","content_rendered":"<h2>概要</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>二线城市小作坊，入职一年多</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>我司前端部门原本没有负责人，一直是我在主导</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>今年春节后，领导开会指定我虚线带队</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>事后找领导谈加薪，让我等到 7 月份</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>想法</h2>\n<p>入职以来我一直有在好好努力提升技能，为公司解决了很多的技术难题，就算不升职也该加薪了。</p>\n<p>当初入职之前谈好的是 13k ，入职后硬是砍了我 1k ，这件事一直让我如鲠在喉。</p>\n<p>想立刻跳槽，但又对‘等 7 月份’这个饼抱有幻想。一直催眠自己，诸如[累积带队经验对以后有帮助]</p>\n<p><strong>各位大佬能不能给点建议，或分享一下类似的经历</strong></p>\n","last_modified":1679307361,"replies":17,"id":925631},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":54442,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1677911181","stars":8282,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":461432,"username":"wangwl999","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/wangwl999","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e99fa088afc88b31f603416e8641668d?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e99fa088afc88b31f603416e8641668d?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e99fa088afc88b31f603416e8641668d?s=73&d=retro","created":1577333210,"last_modified":1577333210},"last_reply_by":"8355","last_touched":1679294620,"title":"分享一个接入 chatGPT 的正则表达式工具","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/925510","created":1679287107,"deleted":0,"content":"https://wangwl.net/static/projects/visualRegex\r\n\r\n类似 chatGPT ，可以语义化的 生成正则、分析正则。\r\n\r\n并且在此基础上，可以直接 在线测试、生成可视化图形。","content_rendered":"<p><a href=\"https://wangwl.net/static/projects/visualRegex\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://wangwl.net/static/projects/visualRegex</a></p>\n<p>类似 chatGPT ，可以语义化的 生成正则、分析正则。</p>\n<p>并且在此基础上，可以直接 在线测试、生成可视化图形。</p>\n","last_modified":1679287191,"replies":17,"id":925510},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/progr